WEBVTT

00:04.787 --> 00:06.093
So, how'd
the date go last night?

00:06.180 --> 00:08.269
Ah, another bait and switch.

00:08.356 --> 00:10.227
Her profile picture
looked like Halle Berry,

00:10.314 --> 00:12.708
but what showed up and ordered
Maine lobster was Chuck Berry.

00:12.795 --> 00:14.057
[laughs]

00:14.144 --> 00:15.580
Well, sorry it didn't work out.

00:15.667 --> 00:18.888
Oh, I didn't say that.
Real nice lady.

00:18.975 --> 00:20.368
Yeah, we-we're gonna go
out to karaoke next week.

00:20.455 --> 00:22.718
You know, she's got
Mr. Berry's face.

00:22.805 --> 00:25.025
Let's see
if she's got his pipes.

00:25.112 --> 00:27.679
Hang on, we got
a car up on the curb.

00:27.766 --> 00:29.029
All right, I'll grab
the Breathalyzer.

00:29.116 --> 00:32.162
[siren chirps]I'll put on my shoes.

00:41.171 --> 00:42.694
Is she drunk or dead?

00:42.781 --> 00:45.088
Well, either way,
she can't park here.

00:45.175 --> 00:46.046
Ma'am?

00:52.748 --> 00:53.836
Glad you're here, Officer.

00:53.923 --> 00:56.621
I'm looking for my car.

00:56.708 --> 00:57.970
Aren't you in it?

00:59.233 --> 01:02.149
[laughs]

01:02.236 --> 01:04.586
Look at that, that's like
when you lose your sunglasses,

01:04.673 --> 01:07.893
and they're on top of your head.

01:07.980 --> 01:11.071
Oh, have a nice day.

01:11.158 --> 01:15.075
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!
Turn it off, turn it off.

01:15.162 --> 01:16.293
Okay, I'm gonna need
to see your license

01:16.380 --> 01:17.338
and registration, please.

01:17.425 --> 01:19.949
I can't do that.Why not?

01:20.036 --> 01:22.256
'Cause I don't have it.Well, where is it?

01:22.343 --> 01:23.692
That's a question.
You should ask the judge

01:23.779 --> 01:26.390
who took it away from me.

01:26.477 --> 01:27.783
All right, I'm gonna have
to ask you to step

01:27.870 --> 01:28.784
out of the vehicle, please.

01:28.871 --> 01:29.741
Well, just what is this

01:29.828 --> 01:31.221
all about, Officer?

01:31.308 --> 01:33.267
This is about driving
under the influence.

01:33.354 --> 01:34.529
Well, I didn't drive, I parked.

01:34.616 --> 01:35.878
I mean, technically I stopped

01:35.965 --> 01:36.922
a crime from happening.

01:37.009 --> 01:38.924
You're welcome.

01:39.011 --> 01:41.884
Well, it doesn't matter
that you're stopped.

01:41.971 --> 01:43.538
What matters is
you've admitted to drinking.

01:43.625 --> 01:45.844
And your keys
are in the ignition.

01:45.931 --> 01:48.934
Oh, so, if I didn't
have the keys

01:49.021 --> 01:51.894
then I would just
be sleeping it off?

01:53.635 --> 01:55.027
That's correct.

01:56.159 --> 01:57.639
There we go.

01:59.249 --> 02:01.121
Nighty-night, Officers.

